â€œBought a quarter of this and still enjoying it, a little goes a long way. Nice and strong strain, definitely best to use this when you're done for the day. â€œThis is a great non heady Indica.  Really low THC levels at a little over 6% but the CBD count is over 20%. Gives that narcotic effect" people talk about when referring to strains as this is predominately body_centric.  Thumbs up on this one even though I won't be want to get out of bed in the morning.â€"

â€œIt is a stupendous strain rich with indica with lavishing trichomes. Its high is relaxing, elucidating, and free wheeling.
